      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.7141041438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、奥山さん\nやけに楽しそうだけど、いいことでもあったのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Okuyama.\nYou have a smile on your face. Did something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今からクリスマスパーティーが楽しみで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! I’m already looking forward to the Christmas party…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これは秘密でした！\nなんでもないです！　今のは忘れて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! That was supposed to be a secret.\nIt was nothing! Please forget I said anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに焦らなくても\n秘密だって言うなら無理には聞かないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to get so worked up.\nIf you say it’s a secret‚ I won’t ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nそういえば質問があるんですけど、いいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nCome to think of it‚ I have a question to ask you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのスケジュールなんですけど\nクリスマスイブが丸一日オフになってますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about TRINITYAiLE’s schedule.\nWe have the whole day of Christmas Eve off‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロにいた頃はクリスマスの時期になると\n毎日寝る暇もないくらい忙しかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was at Van Productions‚ the whole Christmas period\nwas so busy‚ we had no time to sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに移籍した今年は\n結構余裕のあるスケジュールになっていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year‚ now we’re with Hoshimi Productions‚\nthe schedule’s pretty relaxed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "この違いはどうしてなのかなって思ったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been wondering why there’s such a difference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "実際仕事のオファーは沢山来てるんだ\nでも全部受けてたら体がいくつあっても足りないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We actually have lots of job offers coming in.\nBut if we accepted them all‚ you wouldn’t be able to keep up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だから奥山さん達が無理しなくてもすむように\n俺の方で仕事量を調整してるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I adjust the workload\nto avoid overloading you and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか\n気遣ってくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why.\nThank you for taking care of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "タレントの健康管理もマネージャーの仕事だからな\n礼を言われることじゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taking care of the talent’s health is a manager’s job.\nYou don’t have to thank me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "私は子役時代からクリスマスでも仕事をしてたので\nイブが休みなのは凄く嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I was a child actress I’ve always worked even on Christmas‚\nso I’m delighted to have Christmas Eve off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、このままクリスマスイブは\n空けておいてもらえると嬉しいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So if you could keep Christmas Eve free\nI’d be very happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "イブに仕事を入れると何か問題があるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would putting a job on Christmas Eve be a problem?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "問題があると言うか、なんと言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ not exactly a problem‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "とにかくクリスマスイブはお休みで！\nお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But anyway‚ keep Christmas Eve as a day off!\nPlease‚ I’m counting on you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。奥山さんがそこまで言うなら\n仕事を入れないようにするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. If you’re asking like that‚\nI won’t schedule any jobs then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n約束ですからね！　絶対仕事を入れないで下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nThat’s a promise‚ right! You absolutely mustn’t schedule a job on that day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスイブ前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day before Christmas Eve",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
