    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "むすー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*pout*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nどうして私が怒ってるのか分かってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nDo you have any idea why I’m angry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "私、言いましたよね？\nクリスマスイブには仕事を入れないで下さいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you‚ didn’t I?\nPlease don’t put a job on Christmas Eve‚ I said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにどうしてクリスマスイベントに\nトリエルが出演することになってるんですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So why does TRINITYAiLE have to appear\nat a Christmas Eve event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。予定していたアイドルが体調不良で\n参加出来なくなったらしくて急遽代役を頼まれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry. The idol I scheduled is unwell and\ncan’t participate‚ so I was asked to provide a replacement in a hurry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスにトリエルのスケジュールが空いてるのは\n先方にしてみれば奇跡だったんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the client it was a miracle that TRINITYAiLE’s schedule\nwas free on Christmas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "イベントが中止になるかどうかの瀬戸際だから\n先方も必死で、どうしても断り切れなかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a critical moment‚ deciding whether the event would be canceled‚\nso the client was desperate and I couldn’t refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_03_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあクリスマスは忙しいのが普通ですし\n星見プロのみんなも当日は別の仕事がありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it that it’s normal to be busy on Christmas‚\nand everyone else at Hoshimi Productions had other work on the day‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
